    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 style="text-align: left;">前言</h2><div>虽然小时候已经来过很多次北京了，但我还是决定再来一次，再来看一看这座【数据删除】的城市。当然那件事已经过去很久了，所以我这次还是以一个旅客的身份来到北京的。</div><div>大多数人的游记都是按照时间顺序写的，但我的记忆力不允许我这么做，所以我会将游记分成几个部分。</div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><h2 style="text-align: left;">美食</h2><div>我听到过很多人对于北京的食物的负面评价，但对于我来说其实大多都还是能接受的。唯一的问题是北京的食物对于我来说都太咸了，所以就算我很喜欢，但吃完一整份还是很困难的。</div><div><br /></div><div><br /><br /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjaKs6dE1MqRAlcI_IJSjrSNS7irs2BDQgHSrtBsTTWbEWwWEDsuupHg-3noES8VFZvpM-7emNZYK9FcO3NjRtcII6lRK6aLHCIl9ODSdtkBkHFePnwvxtMxBnBbwOs6jjW_DEr6F9L8muje3l6Ty7NsoNntNyunv35hm9FlNUTseocYRn1HugQvvT0_cE/s4096/IMG_20250802_082358.jpg" style="clear: left; margin-bottom: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjaKs6dE1MqRAlcI_IJSjrSNS7irs2BDQgHSrtBsTTWbEWwWEDsuupHg-3noES8VFZvpM-7emNZYK9FcO3NjRtcII6lRK6aLHCIl9ODSdtkBkHFePnwvxtMxBnBbwOs6jjW_DEr6F9L8muje3l6Ty7NsoNntNyunv35hm9FlNUTseocYRn1HugQvvT0_cE/w200-h150/IMG_20250802_082358.jpg" width="200" /></a><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEinPyxayXBWTJs4s1Zjv7fsZzdGvhr576LRPw_MZdFFcLenZcLjBQwyeIiP75mia7QbHJ2ZaLNqBDHSnhueLPh1PTLApv76XUMICBrx31dl19tQPkhYOyWd9B_-OormdjITLyhpD4T5H4t3Ja_elRBxPGbIXqU0VlVObYFGDyddYvWmRchhiUxFazAMm_Y/s4096/IMG_20250802_082509.jpg" style="display: inline; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEinPyxayXBWTJs4s1Zjv7fsZzdGvhr576LRPw_MZdFFcLenZcLjBQwyeIiP75mia7QbHJ2ZaLNqBDHSnhueLPh1PTLApv76XUMICBrx31dl19tQPkhYOyWd9B_-OormdjITLyhpD4T5H4t3Ja_elRBxPGbIXqU0VlVObYFGDyddYvWmRchhiUxFazAMm_Y/w200-h150/IMG_20250802_082509.jpg" width="200" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: left;">最喜欢的两道北京菜，卤煮和炒肝。可能和我喜欢肥肠有关。感觉麻酱和蒜和这些内脏也很搭。</span></div><div style="text-align: left;"></div></div><div><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhjBh8sZSWSAklikHmqMgWnRJ37qS0VPgIqxvSvuIPnmdOxzvH1vnjBrhyEzUziaoU3dg5UVRfj4DBOXwYivTxY5-vS96osUe-SS25lRMrigI6vVbdyeu46son2D76X9R-PtEoxjloGDzYX0Dg1HyD-kD8_KwsTAFa2zxdMtRtosdeylTRqCqXXqRM9qCU/s4096/IMG_20250802_083013.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhjBh8sZSWSAklikHmqMgWnRJ37qS0VPgIqxvSvuIPnmdOxzvH1vnjBrhyEzUziaoU3dg5UVRfj4DBOXwYivTxY5-vS96osUe-SS25lRMrigI6vVbdyeu46son2D76X9R-PtEoxjloGDzYX0Dg1HyD-kD8_KwsTAFa2zxdMtRtosdeylTRqCqXXqRM9qCU/w200-h150/IMG_20250802_083013.jpg" width="200" /></a><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg62dOJ6FehRD8biwU0Ej3eZnrApgRzyKjJedqsaTJScc3TVIHVgQF17bhKrx_uYLNJCnpddFW8GFvK2oKEQtJ0Y5ZeWHahtxMFNvXWPcsbYXtYCOSNC70lsv0xIrPYk0ULhvvYqGVa12VPnD-5clmLAAjBit3iqSQTG2-i3p9jpaSNatIy0CRYZqBQWSA/s4096/IMG_20250802_180957.jpg" style="clear: right; display: inline; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg62dOJ6FehRD8biwU0Ej3eZnrApgRzyKjJedqsaTJScc3TVIHVgQF17bhKrx_uYLNJCnpddFW8GFvK2oKEQtJ0Y5ZeWHahtxMFNvXWPcsbYXtYCOSNC70lsv0xIrPYk0ULhvvYqGVa12VPnD-5clmLAAjBit3iqSQTG2-i3p9jpaSNatIy0CRYZqBQWSA/w200-h150/IMG_20250802_180957.jpg" width="200" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">炸酱面和爆肚也还行，但是我更喜欢重庆对这两种菜的吃法。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhMEgv0QpDV2nR5i1HonFCHdXN8p3QOfy2wc5tFBJ9CAgsHsunZWLjznIcVdC7HdeK8a9S3bH-QfLIHpSHZIGebxJL3T_CdqZAMT6iENReg9mee9pAKoCrLQ1LMGxK9ic0s2zZnn5RS9B6666ZiIUtglqwE7g4EiTZyxv8DB7EFmZ7OTbWIyaFKnW7nyww/s4096/IMG_20250803_174915.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="4096" data-original-width="3072" height="200" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhMEgv0QpDV2nR5i1HonFCHdXN8p3QOfy2wc5tFBJ9CAgsHsunZWLjznIcVdC7HdeK8a9S3bH-QfLIHpSHZIGebxJL3T_CdqZAMT6iENReg9mee9pAKoCrLQ1LMGxK9ic0s2zZnn5RS9B6666ZiIUtglqwE7g4EiTZyxv8DB7EFmZ7OTbWIyaFKnW7nyww/w150-h200/IMG_20250803_174915.jpg" width="150" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">在四季民福和便宜坊两家都吃了烤鸭，都巨贵，感觉和在重庆吃的廉价烤鸭的唯一区别就是鸭皮和面皮：鸭皮确实要酥一点，面皮感觉很高级。但和来福士那家小大董感觉没区别，不懂。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZJKcpwIed5HPE3HzWw960HCWx_csmuCz4UKoZlqNpUNSIckY11rVON5ndAP0xkS1b4IiqE1Zuuk3KTLXQ6fxdLtbfjtu-YnAYeUvWsDbtVNsube4Y8CJWwSibJ6AUDAZBmbZNQ3T9P2GUDzX4P1r8dMRZM1gsFMkALOUUynp4Gg9Jg3uT0KTot_S6dnA/s4096/IMG_20250801_195231.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="4096" data-original-width="3072" height="200" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZJKcpwIed5HPE3HzWw960HCWx_csmuCz4UKoZlqNpUNSIckY11rVON5ndAP0xkS1b4IiqE1Zuuk3KTLXQ6fxdLtbfjtu-YnAYeUvWsDbtVNsube4Y8CJWwSibJ6AUDAZBmbZNQ3T9P2GUDzX4P1r8dMRZM1gsFMkALOUUynp4Gg9Jg3uT0KTot_S6dnA/w150-h200/IMG_20250801_195231.jpg" width="150" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">忘拍涮羊肉的图了，只有个可爱的麻酱。味道还可以，但我个人不太喜欢。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">羊蝎子也顺便说一下，感觉比重庆的难吃很多啊，没有任何味道。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhTfrSeSZ62EM38Rtxv-1PQDQBAlANBtU51rtaKSfZnrX4LMflXsj3HCttwdFzcb5-EH1NwweLYiaineule9zLbrO2H2Q_szrgBkC0JwxFgwC5pg1INfXtIJnb4oEdiGEUz1F0F3N7biLpLYAPr1-pQN429oDGHBPEluQddxGpZNMTfjG4_AKT_7vPORu0/s4096/IMG_20250804_220915.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhTfrSeSZ62EM38Rtxv-1PQDQBAlANBtU51rtaKSfZnrX4LMflXsj3HCttwdFzcb5-EH1NwweLYiaineule9zLbrO2H2Q_szrgBkC0JwxFgwC5pg1INfXtIJnb4oEdiGEUz1F0F3N7biLpLYAPr1-pQN429oDGHBPEluQddxGpZNMTfjG4_AKT_7vPORu0/w200-h150/IMG_20250804_220915.jpg" width="200" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">发明豆汁的人真的是甜菜，差不多就是呕吐物加放了100年的豆浆的味道。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">焦圈感觉和油条很像啊，还行。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div>接下来就是一些在北京吃到的我觉得还行的国外食物</div><div><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEichwYzYWjrHAran0oWqo4fzkhO6Yk48Vc1RDjGQIMN_PUaV6sPVX4OEkoVgibTtuYhIj5wJTHve3vDVI5iC8DyynOTPC4NbARWTesI-hpOpLygv3OQtW2QNj2ZmsnZHjReHdSzgiuRIFcDkJfSNxDOu4ccHXAPcUBFkZEtmuZU1Nnm5cvvsWP6a7biin4/s4096/IMG_20250804_182353.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEichwYzYWjrHAran0oWqo4fzkhO6Yk48Vc1RDjGQIMN_PUaV6sPVX4OEkoVgibTtuYhIj5wJTHve3vDVI5iC8DyynOTPC4NbARWTesI-hpOpLygv3OQtW2QNj2ZmsnZHjReHdSzgiuRIFcDkJfSNxDOu4ccHXAPcUBFkZEtmuZU1Nnm5cvvsWP6a7biin4/w200-h150/IMG_20250804_182353.jpg" width="200" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">在一家格鲁吉亚餐厅吃的鹿肉，口感味道都和牛腱子差不多。但是旁边的饼不知道是何意，感觉和这道菜不是很搭。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiySsFn7eT9wFZlnwJ353MuAeHCDnP7TmcWDlijY5uRwl7A3GUvh9fciDDq3lFSB7HBnvk0zaj26vJCKkVxj6_xgxFvD6YTgPnyzJEGyOGqak6WugluWSeUQS9cZW2BzcQEGMRZqOl4vw6gEgWovKuyKvOcrciIikEEitQFCg2oZ0fV7hH58r-V_1RC59Y/s4096/IMG_20250804_180509.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiySsFn7eT9wFZlnwJ353MuAeHCDnP7TmcWDlijY5uRwl7A3GUvh9fciDDq3lFSB7HBnvk0zaj26vJCKkVxj6_xgxFvD6YTgPnyzJEGyOGqak6WugluWSeUQS9cZW2BzcQEGMRZqOl4vw6gEgWovKuyKvOcrciIikEEitQFCg2oZ0fV7hH58r-V_1RC59Y/w200-h150/IMG_20250804_180509.jpg" width="200" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">很奇特的一道菜，烟熏三文鱼里面加了些生菜丝和一种我不知道是啥的食物，口感像很硬的土豆泥。(<strike>感觉好像是很常见的，也许是我孤陋寡闻</strike>)</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgIw-eCmr1yZn48ikfWAZw97snJy8rSBJGWs3Xze-ksYcDCabnsWvwzIxFIg1WpX0Mfpj1zjoXpRhSxu6-HVXeMo8LlC1qMKcR40ULKiZuxi3sZrXp_3vC7aXPe49pZi1kPZo5tAbgHvyogWFzRPizio32sfwmCZ2khGmJN3PgpOKN2knft26587pfG3do/s4096/IMG_20250805_124900.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgIw-eCmr1yZn48ikfWAZw97snJy8rSBJGWs3Xze-ksYcDCabnsWvwzIxFIg1WpX0Mfpj1zjoXpRhSxu6-HVXeMo8LlC1qMKcR40ULKiZuxi3sZrXp_3vC7aXPe49pZi1kPZo5tAbgHvyogWFzRPizio32sfwmCZ2khGmJN3PgpOKN2knft26587pfG3do/w200-h150/IMG_20250805_124900.jpg" width="200" /></a><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7TQouylAr1wgPvO_63TeQPfDH9IkZ1JqPPxy-JKyvvFYWqQ9OaNRDrWuLnl57VAwLI5LqhIIRHDAubTQMLocDi_FDnX5YDXCqj5WNZc8jsmnKQT6xHB-jJzPHvYM3OysmVe80O3751DtuuSUbxyPNzlVmX3Qw9yhWGy14Vq0DPLxJFcgrXb7ZAE9jwbQ/s4096/IMG_20250805_131034.jpg" style="clear: right; display: inline; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3072" data-original-width="4096" height="150" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh7TQouylAr1wgPvO_63TeQPfDH9IkZ1JqPPxy-JKyvvFYWqQ9OaNRDrWuLnl57VAwLI5LqhIIRHDAubTQMLocDi_FDnX5YDXCqj5WNZc8jsmnKQT6xHB-jJzPHvYM3OysmVe80O3751DtuuSUbxyPNzlVmX3Qw9yhWGy14Vq0DPLxJFcgrXb7ZAE9jwbQ/w200-h150/IMG_20250805_131034.jpg" width="200" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">这两道菜都是在一家好像很火的西餐厅吃的，披萨比较正常，羊排还挺惊艳的。提这家餐厅主要是走的时候送了我一盒价值不菲的饼干。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgzerxlsIR3IksN4FTjcuskawKaF3PJMU76IEBGdQ1hYNUMnOt30GayQethllfW1qHMcUAjwoEmv63rU77fj4dVQIq51gKTWT_RdHAXmrb7XrmVf0mcykMw8-Re9UUKGp3HBBCcTLtW6S4Wy0KumqgxcNitaMJcVyTjarcSIT3zrURG0WKRjlvmKvKRyr0/s4096/IMG_20250803_135918.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="4096" data-original-width="3072" height="200" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgzerxlsIR3IksN4FTjcuskawKaF3PJMU76IEBGdQ1hYNUMnOt30GayQethllfW1qHMcUAjwoEmv63rU77fj4dVQIq51gKTWT_RdHAXmrb7XrmVf0mcykMw8-Re9UUKGp3HBBCcTLtW6S4Wy0KumqgxcNitaMJcVyTjarcSIT3zrURG0WKRjlvmKvKRyr0/w150-h200/IMG_20250803_135918.jpg" width="150" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">很遗憾的是我并没有在北京找到当地的咖啡馆和饮品店，所有只试了试似乎在重庆没有的喜茶黑金店。但是感觉主要的升级在外观，味道并没有很特别。</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><br /></div><h2 style="clear: both; text-align: left;">景点</h2><div>我其实很讨厌去景点，因为人多，还要走很多路。所以虽然北京有许多著名的景点，我这次只打算去地坛公园。（<strike>虽然最后拼尽全力无法战胜资本还是去了长城</strike>）</div><div><br /></div><div><span>&nbsp;<div style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEisPgUABlgMYg-qCLq1m39wcAU32-2rUSaEF8WqBKatz7g0KmxU4wyWEChTTriSpAfX6Zz61BPmDLi1fCLUPu2-Y-KNCbmdwlobShGZ5W7LPFQ9sISuQ8GLQBwQ6wrQmVpoU2QUgwQaP76Yqo8_0AtvHTEpjtG8m0lPNgoJXOqXlrCxDuth97XHwiTMwAA/s4096/IMG_20250804_153330.jpg"><img border="0" data-original-height="4096" data-original-width="3072" height="200" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEisPgUABlgMYg-qCLq1m39wcAU32-2rUSaEF8WqBKatz7g0KmxU4wyWEChTTriSpAfX6Zz61BPmDLi1fCLUPu2-Y-KNCbmdwlobShGZ5W7LPFQ9sISuQ8GLQBwQ6wrQmVpoU2QUgwQaP76Yqo8_0AtvHTEpjtG8m0lPNgoJXOqXlrCxDuth97XHwiTMwAA/w150-h200/IMG_20250804_153330.jpg" width="150" /></a></div><div style="text-align: center;">很奇怪，出发前一周脑子里突然就冒出了这个地名，于是就来了。</div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEip3gucqM8c1tXPwmj1BMYvx78sOsdWeqbcJtm0aQum3E7I6I29pgkKdxyOWZpw5P8pBF7PExWJ0rnpNauNEuEPuEOpAnXKbhKRH34FPNTnj-thTQB6LyP_SiUoW6xEjk0edrllZMhCwHlV0Q4mAMfDY7HohtOspEpdyoSrw7kGpYINPHdzNrblNepyQQA/s1920/wx_camera_1754108003658.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="1920" data-original-width="1080" height="180" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEip3gucqM8c1tXPwmj1BMYvx78sOsdWeqbcJtm0aQum3E7I6I29pgkKdxyOWZpw5P8pBF7PExWJ0rnpNauNEuEPuEOpAnXKbhKRH34FPNTnj-thTQB6LyP_SiUoW6xEjk0edrllZMhCwHlV0Q4mAMfDY7HohtOspEpdyoSrw7kGpYINPHdzNrblNepyQQA/w113-h180/wx_camera_1754108003658.jpg" width="113" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh879k_ULW-D1RnD6w8H_i7fEcG5ifYUV1gIqNDys4Jb5IFPdr_Vh8E9COOIwfdv6a-zeURE5oKpYX2pF_y5ZRX4zIPIQrMoQ9qbq509VZXS0LJkxandB57nhWUoyv_3hBBD8CoFjXq5kxvPRkaR8YYNVXjGClJhhF_dsfJhVEhi7UGpXxuk3juFwt9iSk/s4096/IMG_20250802_115622.jpg" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><br /></a></div></div><div style="text-align: center;">长城没什么可说的，被迫去的。但是这瓶20元的冰红茶，很好。</div><div style="text-align: center;">原来缆车和索道是两个东西。缆车是一个车厢，索道是一张椅子。但为啥重庆长江索道也是车厢啊，不懂。</div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><h2 style="text-align: left;">交通</h2><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span>地铁</span></h3><div><span>人疑似有点过多了，不是很懂为什么饭点还有这么多人。没坐到过位置。</span><br /></div><h3 style="text-align: left;"><span><span>公交</span></span></h3><div><span><span><span>下车扫码还是太先进了。感觉支付方式对于没有银行卡的未成年人还是不太友好。等车时间的中位数大概是20min，不是很懂。</span><br /></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><br /></span></span></span></div><div><span><span><span><br /></span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><i>以后大概率不会再来了，除非......</i></div><br /></span><br /></div>]]></content>
    
    
    
